eslint: Add missing `space-before-keywords` rule

All examples in README.md seem to agree on avoiding missing whitespaces
before keywords such as:

    if (cond) {
    }else {       // no space before 'else'
    }

    try {
    }catch (e) {  // no space before 'catch'
    }

